'''= "an organisation offering support to young laureates invested in bringing radical or far-reaching change"'''

URL: http://www.vocatio.be/nl/composition/

=== Description ===
The main aim of VOCATIO is to offer both material and moral support to creative and intellectual young people who are trying to who are involved in bringing radical and far-reaching change.  Every year the organisation awards fifteen scholarships worth € 10,000 to young people with the purpose of making their visions for change a reality. These scholarships are awarded independent of the person's background, discipline, area of concern or level of study. It is only meant to award a laureate with recognition for their ideas, a springboard for their mission and a new network of contacts to allow them to grow further. 

